wmsLayer.title: GA0339 grid1 2m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is a bathymetry grid of survey grid 1 from marine survey GA0339, collected within the Oceanic Shoals Commonwealth Reserve, north of Western Australia. A total of four areas were surveyed and gridded at two metre resolution. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 40-140 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/79006.
